{"tid":1494912,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"青衣文宣已經不存在","createTime":"2019-08-22T00:00:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T00:51:59.000Z","uid":277735,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"edc9bea3f4e7ed4d72d8b183d64c3f79c75e0ed4","tid":1494912,"uid":277735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T00:00:26.000Z","msg":"對唔住大家🙇🏻&zwj;♂<br />\n青衣文宣已經不存在。<br />\n我會同一班有心做文宣既人繼續努力。而我地係唔需要任何資金。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家都可以繼續互相合作。最近夜晚都好危險，希望大家萬事小心。"},{"pid":"b648007c6192797dd84c04eb094e816228fcbb68","tid":1494912,"uid":254923,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T00:06:31.000Z","msg":"乜春呀 青衣係咪得你地幾個啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"145c50f0f80973ee92232c2dbb6d57126d11748c","tid":1494912,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T00:33:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dec9320d51b223d042a3a161c2a2ecc98c070a30","tid":1494912,"uid":211645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T00:37:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3663526e43af83b9c8f19f191e5eee0eb2fd889e","tid":1494912,"uid":277735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b648007c6192797dd84c04eb094e816228fcbb68","tid":1494912,"uid":254923,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T00:06:31.000Z","msg":"乜春呀 青衣係咪得你地幾個啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T00:51:59.000Z","msg":"&lt;青衣文宣&gt;聲明<br />\n<br />\n本組在此嚴正聲明，從來沒有發起過任何籌款活動，更沒有收受薪金，承諾以後不會接受任何資金援助。<br />\n<br />\n對於被指出&lt;青衣文宣&gt;此名太具代表性而因此令不屬本組的人也覺得被代表了，本組表示理解，因此決定解散&lt;青衣文宣&gt;，從此不再用帶有&lt;青衣&gt;二字來命名。現在的tg谷已成為青衣公海，供其他人作文宣自發召集或傳遞消息用。<br />\n<br />\nAdmin們不會放棄文宣的工作，但新組就不會再公開招人，亦從此次事件中吸取經驗，希望可以往後可以在管理上作出改善。<br />\n<br />\n在此為我們過去的不足致上真誠的道歉，亦感謝所有與我們一起走過、支持過我們、為我們打氣的人，共勉之。"}]}